<font color="undefined" size="NaN">破坏自然出于人的利己主义</font>

307
00:20:24,179 --> 00:20:26,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">保护自然同样也是人利己的体现而已</font>

308
00:20:27,689 --> 00:20:30,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">自然原本就应该不断毁灭与重生</font>

309
00:20:31,259 --> 00:20:34,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">人却硬把它维持在自己想要的状态</font>

310
00:20:35,789 --> 00:20:38,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">人能做的也只能是使用间伐等手段</font>

311
00:20:38,889 --> 00:20:42,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让森林维持在与人和平共处的状态而已</font>

312
00:21:02,129 --> 00:21:04,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这次我什么忙都没帮上啊</font>

313
00:21:05,669 --> 00:21:07,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你不是带救援队伍过来了吗</font>

314
00:21:08,519 --> 00:21:10,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大家都已经尽力了</font>

315
00:21:11,079 --> 00:21:14,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反而是我什么都没做好</font>

316
00:21:14,919 --> 00:21:16,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哪里</font>

317
00:21:16,289 --> 00:21:18,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我听说你出了很多力啊</font>

318
00:21:20,379 --> 00:21:22,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我的身份是国王</font>

319
00:21:22,979 --> 00:21:26,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">出事的时候不应该是我这个国王到现场指挥</font>

320
00:21:26,579 --> 00:21:31,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">国王要做的是在事情发生前做好应对的准备</font>

321
00:21:31,979 --> 00:21:33,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而我没有做好这方面工作</font>

322
00:21:33,849 --> 00:21:36,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你在说什么 你…</font>

323
00:21:37,089 --> 00:21:40,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我以为将禁军编成救援部队这块做得不错</font>

324
00:21:41,209 --> 00:21:43,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但实际上还有很多不足</font>

325
00:21:44,399 --> 00:21:50,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">信息传递手段 长距离运输手段 各地区救援物资的配备</font>

326
00:21:50,209 --> 00:21:52,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">附属于救援部队的医疗团队</font>

327
00:21:53,349 --> 00:21:55,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么都没做好</font>

328
00:21:56,169 --> 00:21:59,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一直专注于粮食短缺和三公爵问题</font>

329
00:21:59,399 --> 00:22:01,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反而遗忘了这些工作</font>

330
00:22:02,529 --> 00:22:03,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">相马…</font>

331
00:22:10,989 --> 00:22:14,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风 穿越整个世界</font>

332
00:22:15,169 --> 00:22:19,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">连接不可能相遇的我们</font>

333
00:22:19,389 --> 00:22:23,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">展开没有人看得见的羽翼</font>

334
00:22:23,599 --> 00:22:27,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">找寻没有人看得见的奇迹</font>

335
00:22:27,529 --> 00:22:30,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">起飞吧</font>

336
00:22:36,429 --> 00:22:40,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">继续迷惘明日的方向</font>

337
00:22:40,619 --> 00:22:44,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">追求继续选择的勇气</font>

338
00:22:44,859 --> 00:22:48,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不曾怀疑天空有多蓝</font>

339
00:22:48,989 --> 00:22:53,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望我能毫不畏惧世事无常</font>

340
00:22:53,589 --> 00:22:55,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起将来的梦想</font>

341
00:22:55,809 --> 00:22:57,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">超越想象中的未来</font>

342
00:22:57,899 --> 00:23:01,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这般时光是如此美好</font>

343
00:23:02,199 --> 00:23:04,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只想徜徉在其中</font>

344
00:23:04,379 --> 00:23:06,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你共同度过现在</font>

345
00:23:06,429 --> 00:23:09,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要是能实现就好了</font>

346
00:23:09,799 --> 00:23:14,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">穿过湛蓝 绵延不断的天空</font>

347
00:23:14,739 --> 00:23:18,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将轮回的命运拉近身边</font>

348
00:23:18,429 --> 00:23:22,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">传达思念给紧握的手</font>

349
00:23:22,849 --> 00:23:27,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仅仅希望这就是永远</font>

350
00:23:27,649 --> 00:23:29,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使现在只是幻影</font>

351
00:23:29,839 --> 00:23:32,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算是在某人的梦境里</font>

352
00:23:32,029 --> 00:23:33,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风</font>

353
00:23:33,759 --> 00:23:38,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在抓住它 起飞吧</font>

